- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper may involve networking and internet architecture considerations when dealing with hybrid cloud environments. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a heuristic algorithm to solve a binary nonlinear programming problem, which may fall under the category of systems and control. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may involve software engineering considerations when designing and implementing the proposed algorithm for managing resources in a hybrid cloud environment.
